=Description=

'Obey' is an essay film by British filmaker Temujin Doran based on the book "The Death of the Liberal Class" by Truthdig columnist Chris Hedges. The explores the rise of the corporate state and the future of obedience in a world filled with unfettered capitalism, worsening inequality and environmental changes.


